#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.arcsinh.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.arcsinh"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:1 of
msgid "Inverse hyperbolic sine element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算反双曲正弦值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播至输入形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:15 of
msgid "**out** -- Tensor of of the same shape as `x`."
msgstr "**out** -- 与 `x` 形状相同的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:19 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:20 of
msgid ""
"`arcsinh` is a multivalued function: for each `x` there are infinitely "
"many numbers `z` such that `sinh(z) = x`. The convention is to return the"
" `z` whose imaginary part lies in `[-pi/2, pi/2]`."
msgstr ""
"`arcsinh` 是一个多值函数：对于每个 `x`，有无穷多个数 `z` 满足 `sinh(z) = "
"x`。约定返回虚部位于 `[-pi/2, pi/2]` 范围内的 `z`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:24 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input data types, `arcsinh` always returns real output. "
"For each value that cannot be expressed as a real number or infinity, it "
"returns ``nan`` and sets the `invalid` floating point error flag."
msgstr ""
"对于实数类型的输入数据，`arcsinh` 总是返回实数输出。对于无法表示为实数或"
"无穷大的值，它返回 ``nan`` 并设置浮点数错误标志 `invalid`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:28 of
msgid ""
"For complex-valued input, `arccos` is a complex analytical function that "
"has branch cuts `[1j, infj]` and `[-1j, -infj]` and is continuous from "
"the right on the former and from the left on the latter."
msgstr ""
"对于复数输入，`arccos` 是一个复数解析函数，具有分支切割 `[1j, infj]` 和 `"
"[-1j, -infj]`，在前一个区间从右侧连续，在后一个区间从左侧连续。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:32 of
msgid "The inverse hyperbolic sine is also known as `asinh` or ``sinh^-1``."
msgstr "反双曲正弦也称为 `asinh` 或 ``sinh^-1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:35 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:36 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I.A. Stegun, \"Handbook of Mathematical Functions\", "
"10th printing, 1964, pp. 86. http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"
msgstr ""
"M. Abramowitz 和 I.A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》，第10版，1964年，第86页。"
"http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arcsinh.arcsinh:38 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Inverse hyperbolic function\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcsinh"
msgstr "维基百科，“反双曲函数”，http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcsinh"

